<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 12-Jan-2026</p>

<p>
Pakistani Drama is developed by Re-creation Technologies.
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect user information
when you use our mobile application available on the Google Play Store.
</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>

<h4>Personal Information</h4>
<p>
We do not collect personally identifiable information such as name, phone number,
or address unless you voluntarily provide it (for example, by contacting support).
</p>

<h4>Non-Personal Information</h4>
<p>
The app may collect non-personal information automatically, including:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Device information (model, manufacturer)</li>
    <li>Android version</li>
    <li>App usage data</li>
    <li>Crash reports and performance logs</li>
</ul>

<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>

<p>
This app uses third-party services that may collect information used to identify you.
These services include:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Google Play Services</li>
    <li>Firebase Analytics</li>
    <li>Firebase Crashlytics</li>
    <li>Google AdMob (for displaying ads)</li>
</ul>

<p>
These services operate under their own privacy policies.
</p>

<h3>Advertising (AdMob)</h3>

<p>
We use Google AdMob to display advertisements.
AdMob may use device identifiers, cookies, or similar technologies to show
personalized or non-personalized ads based on user interests.
</p>

<p>
Users can opt out of personalized ads through their device settings.
</p>

<h3>How We Use Information</h3>

<p>
Collected data is used to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Improve app functionality and performance</li>
    <li>Analyze user behavior and trends</li>
    <li>Fix bugs and crashes</li>
    <li>Serve relevant advertisements</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Security</h3>

<p>
We take reasonable steps to protect your information.
However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage
is 100% secure.
</p>

<h3>Childrenâ€™s Privacy</h3>

